  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in North America, Europe, Asia and Oceania. The purpose of this study
      is to evaluate safety and efficacy of Recombinant Factor VIIa in patients with acute
      intracerebral bleeding.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
